cart.name: Rado Captain Cook

cart.name: Rolex Deepsea
cart.description: Rolex Deepsea is a professional diver’s watch engineered for extreme depths. With a 44mm Oystersteel case, Helium Escape Valve, and water resistance up to 3,900 meters, it’s built for the deep. Powered by the Caliber 3235, it combines strength, precision, and iconic Rolex design.

cart.name: Rolex Sky-Dweller
cart.description: Rolex Sky-Dweller is a sophisticated travel watch built for global citizens. It features a 42mm Oyster case, dual time zone display, and an annual calendar with Saros system. Powered by the Caliber 9001, it offers both elegance and technical mastery—a true blend of innovation and luxury.

wishlist.name: Rolex Daytona
wishlist.description: Rolex Daytona is a world-renowned chronograph, crafted for precision racing timekeeping. Featuring a 40mm Oystersteel case, Cerachrom bezel, and superlative chronometer movement, it delivers unmatched performance and elegance. The Daytona combines luxury style with high-end functionality, making it a true icon in motorsport-inspired watches.

wishlist.name: Rolex Explorer II
wishlist.description: Rolex Explorer II is designed for adventurers and explorers. Featuring a 42mm Oystersteel case, a highly legible 24-hour display, and an independent GMT hand, it’s perfect for navigating day and night. Powered by the Caliber 3285, it delivers robust performance and precision.

wishlist.name: Rolex Submariner
